#!/bin/sh
sudo service gpsd stop
sleep 10
echo -e "\$PMTK300,250,0,0,0,0*35\r\n" > /dev/ttyS0
echo -e "\$PMTK251,38400*27\r\n" > /dev/ttyS0
stty -F /dev/ttyS0 38400
#gpsctl -c 0.25 /dev/ttyS0
sudo service gpsd start
